본 file 은 disease-axis-orthogonal roadmap. hexa-bio 의 5 axis 가 men's health (남성 hypogonadism + ED + BPH expansion + 전립선암 expansion + 남성 contraception + andropause + male infertility + Peyronie + PE + male osteoporosis + gynecomastia + alopecia cross + erectile prosthesis 약리) 에 어떻게 기여하는지 cross-axis mapping + 신규 약물 기준 falsifier inventory.

(Distinct from `.roadmap.disease_urological` — urological 은 BPH AR-axis 중심 narrow; 본 entry 는 male hypogonadism testosterone replacement + ED PDE5 + 남성 contraception + andropause + male infertility 광범위 men's-health-clinical 중심. Distinct from `.roadmap.disease_reproductive` — reproductive 는 ART/IVF/FSH 중심 — 본 entry 는 male-side-only.)

scope:
- 남성 성선기능저하증 (hypogonadism — TRT)
