## 5. raw#10 honest C3

1. **Eroxon MED3000 2024 OTC US** = first OTC ED — gel applied to glans 5-10min, NO-releasing topical bypass systemic PDE5. UK 2023 → US 2024 OTC. ED treatment access paradigm shift. quantum-VQE 의 NO-cGMP topical kinetics modeling 한정.
2. **TRT TRAVERSE trial 2024 (NEJM)** = TRT 의 CV safety 장기 논쟁 reassurance. ~5200 men with hypogonadism + CV risk, MACE 비-열등성 입증. 임상 prescribing 변화.
3. **oral testosterone undecanoate trio (Jatenzo 2019 / Tlando 2022 / Kyzatrex 2022)** = lymphatic absorption bypass hepatic 1st-pass + 17α-alkyl hepatotoxicity 회피. modern oral TRT 부활. quantum-VQE 의 lymphatic chylomicron 결합 한정.
4. **PDE5 quartet (sildenafil 1998 / vardenafil 2003 / tadalafil 2003 / avanafil 2012)** + tadalafil daily BPH dual indication 2011 — ED 약리 성숙. avanafil rapid 15min Tmax 가 next-gen pocket selectivity.
5. **collagenase clostridium hist Xiaflex 2013** = first FDA Peyronie's. 음경 plaque collagen 분해 + intralesional injection. 외과 절제술 alternative. quantum docking 의 collagen substrate modeling 한정.
6. **2nd-gen AR antagonist 4-pack (enzalutamide 2012 / apalutamide 2018 / darolutamide 2019 / + 2024 N-desmethyl metabolite research)** + abiraterone CYP17A1 2011 + relugolix Orgovyx oral GnRH antag 2020 + Lu-177-PSMA-617 Pluvicto 2022 = 전립선암 11+ 년 임상 paradigm 변화 (cross-cancer + cross-palliative). darolutamide 2024 ARANOTE mHSPC label expansion.
7. **남성 contraception NES/T daily gel (Phase 2/3) + DMAU oral (Phase 2) + 11β-MNTDC** = 60+ 년 male contraceptive vacuum 끝낼 candidate. progestin + androgen 조합 spermatogenesis 억제. 2025-2027 expected approval window.
8. **dapoxetine PE EU/global, no US FDA** = 조루 on-demand SSRI rapid Tmax + short t1/2. 미국 시장 unmet — paroxetine off-label 만 가능. 약리경제 + regulatory anomaly.
9. **bremelanotide Vyleesi 2019** = HSDD female MC4R agonist. 남성 trial 진행 중 (libido + ED 보조). MC-axis 가 신규 mechanism for both sexes.
10. **wet-lab + clinical RCT 없음** — quantum-only in-silico, men's-health 임상 의미 한정.

